                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180909-320-off1759 t18180909-320-cd1760"></join>, one watch, value 6l.; two seals, value 6d., and two keys, value 6d., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18180909-320-victim2211" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Everleigh
                        <interp inst="t18180909-320-victim2211" type="surname" value="Everleigh"></interp>
